! <<lingo Name>>

<<lingo Description>>

!! FAQ

V0.4.0+ use Tldraw 2.0.0, which is not compatible with previous version. So if your wiki have some old drawings, you need to re-draw them, or use previous version of this plugin, or open old file with tldraw vscode plugin or its official website, to let it upgrade your file.
